entries.do_not_edit: The English version of this file (npe_entertainer_1_questgiver.stf) is automatically generated by the SwgConversationEditor.
entries.s_14: You are an entertainer, aren't you? I'm glad you're here! Do you have time for a quick dance set?
entries.s_16: I can always use the extra credits.
entries.s_18: Great! I need to bring in customers and you are the person to do it! Please head onto the stage or into the crowd and dance. With your apparent grace, you should draw up a nice crowd.
entries.s_20: What are the exact terms of the agreement?
entries.s_22: I can pay you 250 credits. If you would do two 20-second dance routines, I'd be grateful.
entries.s_26: Wonderful! Come back to me when you are done.
entries.s_32: I'm done. The crowd was small, but they loved me. Did you watch?
entries.s_34: I did and you were great! I can't wait to see all the dances you will learn in the future. Maybe I'll run into you again. Thank you. Here is your payment.
entries.s_38: Well then get back up there. We've got a show to do!
entries.s_39: Thank you for everything! You have some real potential, %TU!
entries.s_41: No thanks. I'm busy right now.
entries.s_44: I understand. This isn't the most glamorous cantina in the galaxy. Come back if you change your mind.
